author: blair
msg: In the section of svnserve.conf describing the passwd and the
authz files, change the language to state that the location of
these files are relative to the svnserve.conf file, not the conf
directory, since with svnserve's new --config-file option, the
svnserve.conf file can be located anywhere and the passwd and
authz are relative to the dirname of svnserve.conf.
